{"id":460154,"name":"","username":"ndruha","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/ndruha/{size}/28049_2.png","created_at":"2025-12-30T13:30:34.182Z","cooked":"<p>Hello again <img src=\"https://forum.magicball.net/uploads/default/original/3X/4/e/4ea3bc36966a1229e68a7cc329bf65ad8b65c254.png\" alt=\"\" data-base62-sha1=\"bdG2IdgPHz2DAuJpNa566IgIV3m\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"> Some news here for the last moments of this year. I have recorded a video tutorial for IdaJS. Here I show how we install IdaJS on your PC, and how to create your very first mod.</p>\n<p>In this tutorial, we will create together a secret dialog with Baldino on the radio. Both English and French subtitles are available for this video.</p>\n<p>            <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XiBlQ5rBOGE?feature=oembed&amp;wmode=opaque\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"youtube-onebox\" seamless=\"seamless\" sandbox=\"allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-presentation\"></iframe>\n</p>\n<p>The old pre-release discussion, about what is IdaJS is here: <a href=\"https://forum.magicball.net/t/lba2-mod-innerbytes/30154\" class=\"inline-onebox\">LBA2 mod innerbytes</a></p>\n<p>See also more information here:</p><aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://innerbytes.com\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://forum.magicball.net/uploads/default/original/3X/0/7/078f99b4070ab2c90bc0eaae0ca4985c049dc961.png\" class=\"site-icon\" alt=\"\" data-dominant-color=\"753533\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://innerbytes.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Innerbytes Software</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:690/361;\"><img src=\"https://forum.magicball.net/uploads/default/optimized/3X/2/7/279aae77ec4701b27fb5da66bcbb30eda43eb48f_2_690x362.png\" class=\"thumbnail\" alt=\"\" data-dominant-color=\"D7D3CE\" width=\"690\" height=\"362\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://innerbytes.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Innerbytes Software - Games, Mods &amp; Software Development</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Creating games, mods, and innovative software projects. Actual: IdaJS mod engine for Little Big Adventure 2.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n","post_number":1,"post_type":1,"posts_count":6,"updated_at":"2025-12-30T13:35:38.418Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":1,"reads":24,"readers_count":23,"score":84.8,"yours":false,"topic_id":30207,"topic_slug":"mod-lba2-with-idajs-getting-started-video-tutorial","display_username":"","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":2,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":"","bookmarked":false,"raw":"Hello again ![|16x16](upload://bdG2IdgPHz2DAuJpNa566IgIV3m.png) Some news here for the last moments of this year. I have recorded a video tutorial for IdaJS. Here I show how we install IdaJS on your PC, and how to create your very first mod. \n\nIn this tutorial, we will create together a secret dialog with Baldino on the radio. Both English and French subtitles are available for this video.\n\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XiBlQ5rBOGE\n\nThe old pre-release discussion, about what is IdaJS is here: https://forum.magicball.net/t/lba2-mod-innerbytes/30154\n\nSee also more information here:\nhttps://innerbytes.com","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"count":3,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":f